fields.description:
Expose the UIScrollView setScrollEnabled property to the JavaScript.

Code in TiUIScrollView.m

{code:title=TiUIScrollView.m}
-(void)setScrollEnabled_:(id)args
{
	[[self scrollView] setScrollEnabled:[TiUtils boolValue:args def:YES]];
}
{code}

Javascript could would be:
{code}
var scroll = Ti.UI.createScrollView({
    scrollEnabled: false
});
{code}
